<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q11_v6" title="Q11_v6" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceB</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float">
    <qti-default-value>
      <qti-value>0</qti-value>
    </qti-default-value>
  </qti-outcome-declaration>
  <qti-item-body>
    <p>En una tarjeta de receta se indica la siguiente regla para calcular el volumen total de agua en mililitros:</p>
    <div>
      <m:math>
        <m:mi>V</m:mi>
        <m:mo>=</m:mo>
        <m:mn>250</m:mn>
        <m:mo>·</m:mo>
        <m:mi>t</m:mi>
      </m:math>
    </div>
    <p>En la tarjeta se aclara que <m:math><m:mi>t</m:mi></m:math> es el número de tazas de agua y <m:math><m:mi>V</m:mi></m:math> es el volumen total en mililitros.</p>
    <p>Si se llenan 7 tazas de agua y se sabe que <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mtext> litro</m:mtext><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1000</m:mn><m:mtext> mililitros</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:math>, ¿cuántos litros de agua se usan en total?</p>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="true" max-choices="1">
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">1750 litros<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Con 7 tazas se obtiene <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>250</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>7</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1750</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> mililitros. Como <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>1000</m:mn><m:mtext> mililitros</m:mtext><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mtext> litro</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:math>, entonces <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>1750</m:mn><m:mtext> mililitros</m:mtext><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1,75</m:mn><m:mtext> litros</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:math>, no 1750 litros.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">1,75 litros<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! Con 7 tazas se obtiene <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>250</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>7</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1750</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> mililitros. Luego, como <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>1000</m:mn><m:mtext> mililitros</m:mtext><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mtext> litro</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:math>, se convierte <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>1750</m:mn><m:mtext> mililitros</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:math> a litros: <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>1750</m:mn><m:mo>÷</m:mo><m:mn>1000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1,75</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> litros.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">0,175 litros<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Con 7 tazas se obtiene <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>250</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>7</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1750</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> mililitros. Al convertir a litros, <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>1750</m:mn><m:mo>÷</m:mo><m:mn>1000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1,75</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> litros. Por lo tanto, <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>0,175</m:mn><m:mtext> litros</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:math> no corresponde a <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>1750</m:mn><m:mtext> mililitros</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">0,25 litros<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. El valor <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>0,25</m:mn><m:mtext> litros</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:math> corresponde a <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>250</m:mn><m:mtext> mililitros</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:math>, es decir, a 1 taza. Pero el problema indica 7 tazas, y <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>250</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>7</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1750</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> mililitros, que equivalen a <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>1,75</m:mn><m:mtext> litros</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 1: Reemplazar el número de tazas en la regla</strong></p>
            <p>La regla dada es:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mi>V</m:mi>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>250</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>·</m:mo>
                  <m:mi>t</m:mi>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>Como se llenan 7 tazas, entonces:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mi>V</m:mi>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>250</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>·</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>7</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 2: Calcular el volumen en mililitros</strong></p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mi>V</m:mi>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>250</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>·</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>7</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>1750</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>Por lo tanto, el volumen total es 1750 mililitros.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 3: Convertir mililitros a litros</strong></p>
            <p>Se sabe que:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>1</m:mn>
                  <m:mtext> litro</m:mtext>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>1000</m:mn>
                  <m:mtext> mililitros</m:mtext>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>Entonces, para pasar de mililitros a litros, se divide por 1000:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>1750</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>÷</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>1000</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>1,75</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p>
            <p>En total se usan 1,75 litros de agua.</p>
            <p>La alternativa correcta es la B.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>